Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以惩罚就是命令他们两人去买点心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说他们两个\N在这么冷的天里去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天气可是很冷的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你的穿着看起来也很不保暖耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我没问题喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,古泉同学真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虚就不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我来打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想调戏实玖瑠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就要先打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说你想跟我一战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止在社团教室里战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为实玖瑠很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要是实玖瑠掉在自动贩卖机旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,会想要捡起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是把我比喻成小猫还是零钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谈论可爱东西的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,居然没提到我家的长门同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要比这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我就接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在长门同学睡觉的时候去跟她讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她会叫我「妈妈」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会感冒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 再让我睡一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？那不是假设的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你讲的是真话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,实玖瑠追猫的时候会撞到电线杆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,望着天空的时候会掉进水沟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还百发百中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别说得我好像每天都会发生这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我偶尔会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,长门每天会在浴室的镜子前\N看着自己的肚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是要比谁丢脸对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你连这都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就拿出压箱宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其实实玖瑠的胸上有颗星形的痣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,出现我不知道的情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤屋学姐还真是有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,居然说出连本人都不知道的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去就要输啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别再煽风点火了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓同学 这样就够了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道其他怪事了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,长门同学为了迎接即将到来的情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,偷偷买好材料藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欢度节庆也是好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事没什么好难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没必要偷偷做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:24.43,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ナゾナゾみたいな恋してみるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.97,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星が囁く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.89,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}怖いけど…ありかな！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:35.36,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}なんとなく生きてる　なんてつまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.11,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}本当は何かを変えてみたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.82,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}きっかけが欲しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.49,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}飛んで飛んでBoooon！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.66,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}思い出が騒いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:55.25,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}私…あなたを知ってるみたい！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.38,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}晴れても雨でも雪の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.13,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}会いに会いに行っちゃいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.55,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ムカシ→ミライ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.80,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}アシタ→ミライ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.68,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}そうだね　時はNonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:13.48,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}ちょっと前に悩んでたこと　みんなみんな消しちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:19.36,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}新しい物語　始めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:24.45,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}また夢見てる？いまの夢はまだ秘密！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.28,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}晴れ晴れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.95,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}降れ降れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:35.04,OP - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}どんな天気だって I need you！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:24.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想试着谈场猜谜般的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.97,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.89,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}虽然害怕…但还是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:35.36,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安稳度日 也太无趣了点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.11,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改变些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.82,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.49,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飞奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.66,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回忆在骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:55.25,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像认识你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.38,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不论是晴天雨天还是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.13,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.55,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从过去到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.80,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从明天到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.68,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 时间 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:13.48,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前烦恼的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:19.36,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}来展开新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:24.45,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做梦吗？现在的梦还不能说！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.28,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}大晴天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.95,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:35.04,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎样的天气 I need you!!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,平安时代的恋爱很讲究家世财力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是如果和歌写得不好\N就不会受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}会这样是因为当时的恋爱是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}借由和歌往来书信而开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}要先认同对方写和歌的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虚同学 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还蛮痛的 有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}才终于能够进展到约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 今天呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:05.95,Note,,0,0,0,,情人节手作甜点特集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要求得抛物线跟直线交点的座标…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,特地跑来校门前等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是相当体贴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？只有你一个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,古泉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他似乎有委员会的工作所以来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓和长门似乎也有要事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,光我一个人去社团教室也很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以今天社团活动休息一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,于是乎为了别让你闯进学校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,居然不跟本部长商量就擅自休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你这非法社员在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 今天是13号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪要休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的年轻人请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这位女学生有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,少废话 总之跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不 所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说我想赶紧动手开始做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过材料还真是多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有句话叫作\N「只要耐心等待就会有好报」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那句话已经太老旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这不是新旧的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,依我来看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被说成是不可思议的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是不会那么容易出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为这样才有去寻找它的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,必须由我们主动去把\N不可思议的事情找出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那些「好报」也肯定\N一直在等我们把它们找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能这些「好报」\N寻求的是平静与安稳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去找出这世上不可思议的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要上哪找？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这你就不懂了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道也有不知道的找法喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,总之我们就脚踏实地开始探索市区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你将会成为开拓崭新历史的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 随你高兴啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 这样就准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,话说我还没问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做怎样的巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,光看这些材料\N似乎不是要做太复杂的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,总之融化 倒进去 撒上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等凝固以后就变巧克力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说 分明是非常简单的步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但若是让她一个人做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好像会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,简洁明了虽然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但要不要再下点功夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,比方说做个心型巧克力蛋糕之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,心…不用做到那样…没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,太过简单的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就没有我能帮上忙的地方了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也罢 那就赶快来融巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,长门同学加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好 暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里得使用隔水加热的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,隔水加热？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不这么做就没办法顺利融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 真的融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,果然有很多地方需要我帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 那可是二月的河水耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你这样会感冒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该上岸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,再一下下 等我找到河童
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你呆子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别走到太深的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,万一滑倒可是会死的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你干么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是体贴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你双脚好像很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给我记住了 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会记恨的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是这种感觉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,做得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我说阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得河童真的存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,春日？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 区区个阿虚别走在我前面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要去哪里探索？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就放进冰箱等它们凝固啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行 不可以熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你又照例因为睡不着玩起游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等回神时天已经亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你这孩子真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快给我去洗脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,长门同学 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,长门同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是说你什么时候要把巧克力给他？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是社团活动的时间吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就得制造让你们两人独处的空间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,两人独处？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 把阿虚同学叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉难度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不管用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想把巧克力交给他本来就有难度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才多上一两个依然很简单啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,反正不管难度增加多少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是会把那个送给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我会送出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,情人节终于来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虚你说是不是搞错了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谷口 过度期待会带来更深的失望喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的午餐是巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿虚你说是不是搞错了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谷口 死心能防止自己\N受到不必要的伤害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,长门唷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 要去吃午餐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么没跟朝瞄在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤屋同学 不要突然就跑起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟朝仓同学说好在社团教室碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就在文艺社吃午餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,实玖瑠没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是没问题啦 在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以去打扰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没间题 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天待在教室会提心吊胆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉会吃不下饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,提心吊胆？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不就是情人节吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,男生们的眼神都变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤屋同学 你说得太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去要是连一个巧克力都不送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是会演变成不可收拾的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟实玖瑠的粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可是有上百名会员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,知道的真是详细…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们该不会有准备巧克力吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不否认？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…虽说是很理所当然的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过收到的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,会期待喜欢的人送自己巧克力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当然会期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就是为此才存在的节庆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,装作一副不在意的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就证明那个人其实很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那所以拿到其他人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就只会让本人感到困扰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤屋同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以当然会有喜欢 普通\N以及讨厌等等的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那种事根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这本来就是送的人\N单方面的自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就当作是为了自己而送就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,用不着在意对方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就尽情扔到对方怀中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不能用扔的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 我忘记买饮料了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去买一下 你们就先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她应该很快就回来了 我们先吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn华康方圆体W7\fsp10\shad8.5\c&HF2C4EE&\3c&H9F4765&\4c&HA36379&\4a255\iclip(699,984,1246,1065)\t(27,694,\iclip(1246,984,1244,1065))}不说话光吃饭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.68,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn华康方圆体W7\fsp10\shad8.5\c&HD0C5FC&\3c&H7158A6&\4c&H5A4BD2&\4a255\iclip(736,982,1208,1064)\t(26,484,\iclip(1208,982,1208,1064))}似乎很焦虑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我说那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚鹤屋同学是在鼓励你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不是在欺负你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…虽然她说话的方式很极端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 如果换成我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果我是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,收到长门学妹的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么好像变成我在告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法好好表达 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 这位太太你听见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,清清楚楚地听见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎么看都像是告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,实玖瑠？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这话有点难开口 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,长门的心里已经住着阿虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,招来了天大的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要偷听？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟鹤屋学姐在途中碰到就一起过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,结果看到你们两个像\N少女漫画那样对望 不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就用眼神交流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,决定「就这样在旁边看着她们两个吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这两人的思考模式是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是宝冢歌剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,受到学姐们的鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多少有点勇气了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,决战时刻就在放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:29.60,Note,,0,0,0,,情人节大作战！!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在就开始讲述今天的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细听好啰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 长门同学你吧\N社团教室的钥匙拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放学后我会把这支钥匙交给阿虚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请他去开社团教室的门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}我开门啰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在阿虚同学打开教室门的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你再过去的话 接着不可思议的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,社团教室就变成你跟阿虚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,两人独处的空间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会晚一点才去社团教室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 你现在就这么紧张怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧？真的做得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？不过不用绕这么一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我赶快去社团教室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里等他不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,长门同学 你仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得由自己决定何时进入\N有阿虚同学在的教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在教室里战战兢兢地等着\N不知何时才会来的阿虚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一种情况你会比较有心理准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我选自己进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说即使要多花一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也要做好心理准备再送出去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟那是你拼命竭尽心力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所做出的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我被踢进名为「失望」的地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,国木田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只有收到人情巧克力喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就尽情扔到对方怀中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟那是你拼命竭尽心力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所做出的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我来迟了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:42.04,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}名前を呼ばれただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:48.59,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}胸が熱くなるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:53.72,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}近くにいるしあわせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:58.77,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}ああ手放せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:06.15,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}恋は優しい風を連れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.12,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}あしたを夢見る風を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:18.37,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}伝えたいときめきが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:24.54,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}私を変えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:30.55,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}言葉が出てこないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:36.68,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}いつか伝えなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:42.56,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}ありがとう　だいすき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:52.66,ED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}もう少しこのままでいさせて
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:42.04,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}光是听见你呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:48.59,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}胸口就开始发烫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:53.72,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}近在咫尺的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:58.77,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}啊　我不会松手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:06.15,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}恋爱带来温柔的清风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.12,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}那是梦想着明日的清风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:18.37,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}想要传递出的这份悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:24.54,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}改变了原先的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:30.55,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}虽然现在还不知该如何表达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:36.68,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}但总有一天一定要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:42.56,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}谢谢你　最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:52.66,ED - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(198,198)}现在就暂且维持现状吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
